data.description: Step into your dream location through the inviting entry, adorned with an impressive 8' tall front door. Enjoy 9' ceilings with recessed LED lights, creating modern ambiance throughout. This home features a den/office with French doors, 2 large windows, and is wired for cable and ethernet perfect for working from your new home. The open floor plan includes a cozy gas fireplace, an over-the-mantle TV mount, and built-in shelving in the living room. Entertain effortlessly in the eat-in dining area overlooking the peaceful backyard through an expansive 8' tall sliding glass door with an XL built-in pet entrance, perfect for your furry family members. The gourmet kitchen boasts high-end appliances including a gas range and convection oven, a large granite countertop, a stylish and modern tiled backsplash, and a spacious walk-in pantry. Step outside to the covered patio with recessed lighting that is perfect for warm summer and fall evenings. Thought was put into the layout with a mudroom off the garage for added convenience. Upstairs, find a loft wired for ethernet/cable and a mini bar area, perfect for nights spent indoors. Enjoy the accessibility of the upstairs laundry room and the added whole house fan for total comfort. The primary suite features a 5-piece bathroom and a walk-in closet with custom luxury built-ins providing ample storage. Finding a home like this in heart of Fort Collins is rare - schedule a tour today!
